{"tid":737904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 有人網上自稱區議員，其實算唔算冒認公職人員？","createTime":"2018-07-11T06:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T06:54:12.000Z","uid":38910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"568e3d7171d5518cc0a13ee11feb06d385c67a2a","tid":737904,"uid":38910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我發現有個落選民建聯區議員係上屆敗選後，直到今日，係個人網站都一直自稱係民選區議員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.poonchunyuen.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.poonchunyuen.com%2F&d=ePjZ8s8nzOd0IjjNpBSjj10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c6456b27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.poonchunyuen.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144654_20ce96980d028fa59fe8cba599fab6cf.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144654_20ce96980d028fa59fe8cba599fab6cf.PNG&h=9ab0c03f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係佢唔記得咗個網站？<br />\n又唔係wo，因為佢個個人網站係有更新過：<br />\n<br />\n1.佢今年2月先更新過網址註冊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144707_bd6e319e62c32b9267cd8c1f66144bc3.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144707_bd6e319e62c32b9267cd8c1f66144bc3.PNG&h=8e6eefbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.佢個辦公室地址都已經更改為落選後的地址<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144822_f09ad13c905998790846b5832211b8cf.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144822_f09ad13c905998790846b5832211b8cf.PNG&h=56b473bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯獨係佢個網站銜頭無更改過，一直自稱係民選區議員。<br />\n<br />\n如果參考香港法例第228章簡易程序治罪條例第22條： 假冒公職人員或假裝能影響公職人員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144836_4230fb236cafebd1f23ffdbf407131fe.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144836_4230fb236cafebd1f23ffdbf407131fe.PNG&h=62ce2267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無熟悉法律嘅巴絲，可以話我知其實佢算唔算係犯咗法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144849_62b4a0b6e9f3a65e7f7d0e687d392a1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144849_62b4a0b6e9f3a65e7f7d0e687d392a1c.jpg&h=db5744d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/144854_e155b6712f9d941fb89ac0888d0aeba0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F144854_e155b6712f9d941fb89ac0888d0aeba0.jpg&h=ee9d8a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢兩幅相係來自佢個網站，證明呢個網站係佢本人嘅"}]}